# Optional: copy this file to .env to customize the stack.
#
# Used only on first start, when the init container generates the identity —
# it has no effect once this data exists.

# What to Choose
# ===============
# Choose a globally trusted domain (like Microsoft or Apple) that is fully
# unblocked in your country and handles heavy traffic. It must be a domain that your
# local internet provider lets you access freely without a VPN.
#
# How It Is Used
# ===============
# The SNI domain acts as a camouflage, tricking firewalls into seeing a
# legitimate connection to a whitelisted website while routing your
# data through the proxy tunnel.
#
# Note: the camouflage domain is only used for disguise — your traffic is
# never routed through it.
#
# Top Camouflage Domains
# - www.microsoft.com: Microsoft's main website; perfectly mimics everyday browsing traffic.
# - aspnetcdn.com: Microsoft's asset network; excellent for masking encrypted data transfers.
# - www.apple.com: Delivers media assets to millions of Apple devices daily.
# - swcdn.apple.com: Handles software updates for Apple operating systems.
#
SNI_DOMAIN=www.microsoft.com
